# Shared Models Policy

All shared models (API request/response interfaces, database models, enums, types) must live in `packages/shared/src/`.

## Creating new models

1. Create the file in `packages/shared/src/` following the existing directory structure
2. Export it from `packages/shared/src/index.ts`
3. Import from `@fotello/shared` in both frontend and backend

## Do NOT create models in these locations

- `apps/web/models/` — legacy location, being migrated
- `apps/backend/functions/src/models/` — legacy location, being migrated

Existing files in these directories are legacy and will be migrated incrementally. Never add new files there.

## BaseApiRequest

All API request interfaces must extend `BaseApiRequest` from `@fotello/shared`. The `teamId` field is required.
